# bayesian_statistics_project
This repo contains the project of the Course Bayesian Statistics at Politecnico di Milano of the students Contini Matteo, Fiorello Lorenzo and Pasquale Angelo. The code is inside the folder "code"; inside, there are other folder. "main.R" and "simulation_gjam.R". The folder "steps_R" contains eight R functions, each one computing a full conditional needed in the gibbs sampler. The folder "steps_Rcpp" is the same but the functions are written in Rcpp. The folder "src" contains other functions needed. 
